B.GM=s(["Tetralogy of Fallot","Endocardial cushion defect","Coarctation of the aorta","Ventricular septal defect"],t.s)
B.P7=new A.t("Which cardiac defect is most commonly associated with Trisomy 21 (Down syndrome)?",B.GM,1,"Endocardial cushion defect (atrioventricular septal defect) is the most common cardiac defect in Down syndrome. Coarctation of the aorta is associated with Turner syndrome.")
