B.OV=new A.t("The ATNR (asymmetric tonic neck reflex) should integrate by what age?",B.Jq,1,"The ATNR normally integrates by 4-6 months. Persistence beyond this age interferes with midline hand function and rolling. An obligatory ATNR (locked in fencer posture for >30 seconds) is always pathological at any age.")
