B.Op=new A.t("The M-CHAT-R/F is an ASD-specific screening tool recommended by the AAP at which ages?",B.K_,2,"The AAP recommends universal ASD screening with the M-CHAT-R/F at 18 and 24 months. The M-CHAT-R/F is a 20-item parent-report questionnaire for ages 16-30 months with a Follow-Up interview that substantially reduces the false-positive rate.")
